WEBVTT

c0000000
00:00:46.130 --> 00:00:49.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TOGETHER] This is the tale
of our last crusade.</b></Default>

c0000001
00:00:49.090 --> 00:00:50.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA] Or...</b></Default>

c0000002
00:00:50.180 --> 00:00:52.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
The rise of a new world.</b></Default>

c0000003
00:00:57.020 --> 00:00:58.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE FRONT DESK CLERK 201A]
Thank you for your business.</b></Default>

c0000004
00:00:58.480 --> 00:00:59.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Safe travels!</b></Default>

c0000005
00:00:59.730 --> 00:01:02.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[footsteps]</b></Default>

c0000006
00:01:02.690 --> 00:01:04.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
Sisbell! There you are!</b></Default>

c0000007
00:01:05.860 --> 00:01:07.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Can I help you?</b></Default>

c0000008
00:01:07.190 --> 00:01:09.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SISBELL]
What do you want, Alice?</b></Default>

c0000009
00:01:09.240 --> 00:01:11.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We're going home now!</b></Default>

c0000010
00:01:11.200 --> 00:01:12.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>After the battle,
it's not safe.</b></Default>

c0000011
00:01:12.910 --> 00:01:14.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I will not return.</b></Default>

c0000012
00:01:14.570 --> 00:01:17.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sisbell...we're going back!</b></Default>

c0000013
00:01:17.790 --> 00:01:19.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Back off!
-[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000014
00:01:19.330 --> 00:01:21.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll be fine,
I have a bodyguard.</b></Default>

c0000015
00:01:21.920 --> 00:01:23.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000016
00:01:23.170 --> 00:01:25.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-A bodyguard?
-[chuckles]</b></Default>

c0000017
00:01:25.670 --> 00:01:26.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You mean Schwartz?</b></Default>

c0000018
00:01:26.960 --> 00:01:29.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Quit meddling
in my affairs, sister!</b></Default>

c0000019
00:01:29.260 --> 00:01:31.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mother is worried
about you, Sisbell!</b></Default>

c0000020
00:01:31.300 --> 00:01:32.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SISBELL]
I know.</b></Default>

c0000021
00:01:32.590 --> 00:01:35.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Which is why I need you
to deliver this letter to her.</b></Default>

c0000022
00:01:35.430 --> 00:01:37.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, aren't you prepared?</b></Default>

c0000023
00:01:37.510 --> 00:01:40.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're not just
my sister anymore.</b></Default>

c0000024
00:01:40.310 --> 00:01:42.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We're rivals, now!</b></Default>

c0000025
00:01:42.100 --> 00:01:45.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We're competing for the crown,
and my knight in shining armor.</b></Default>

c0000026
00:01:45.940 --> 00:01:47.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I refuse to yield!</b></Default>

c0000027
00:01:47.860 --> 00:01:50.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[footsteps]</b></Default>

c0000028
00:01:51.950 --> 00:01:54.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]
Wait! This bodyguard of yours.</b></Default>

c0000029
00:01:54.410 --> 00:01:56.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If it isn't Schwartz,
don't tell me</b></Default>

c0000030
00:01:56.580 --> 00:01:58.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you're talking about Iska?</b></Default>

c0000031
00:01:58.200 --> 00:01:59.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000032
00:01:59.870 --> 00:02:01.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is something wrong?</b></Default>

c0000033
00:02:01.500 --> 00:02:03.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, uh, it's nothing.</b></Default>

c0000034
00:02:03.500 --> 00:02:05.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, guys, check this out.</b></Default>

c0000035
00:02:05.460 --> 00:02:08.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Our battle...it's on the news.</b></Default>

c0000036
00:02:08.340 --> 00:02:10.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000037
00:02:10.840 --> 00:02:12.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[JHIN] After countless
brushes with death,</b></Default>

c0000038
00:02:12.550 --> 00:02:15.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we finally catch a break,
and then this happens.</b></Default>

c0000039
00:02:15.140 --> 00:02:17.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm so sorry.</b></Default>

c0000040
00:02:17.680 --> 00:02:19.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why are you sitting
on your heels?</b></Default>

c0000041
00:02:19.640 --> 00:02:21.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
It's an expression of shame.</b></Default>

c0000042
00:02:21.480 --> 00:02:22.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't feel bad.</b></Default>

c0000043
00:02:22.640 --> 00:02:25.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The Sovereignty attacked us
outside of the battlefield.</b></Default>

c0000044
00:02:25.480 --> 00:02:28.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And of course, the witch Iska
set free a year ago</b></Default>

c0000045
00:02:28.150 --> 00:02:30.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>just so happened
to be at this resort.</b></Default>

c0000046
00:02:30.150 --> 00:02:32.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>God, what are the chances?</b></Default>

c0000047
00:02:32.110 --> 00:02:35.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It really was a coincidence.
No way we could have known.</b></Default>

c0000048
00:02:35.700 --> 00:02:36.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[JHIN]
You got that right.</b></Default>

c0000049
00:02:37.080 --> 00:02:39.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If it wasn't coincidence,
that means we dropped the ball</b></Default>

c0000050
00:02:39.280 --> 00:02:40.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and got tailed.</b></Default>

c0000051
00:02:40.540 --> 00:02:42.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And I don't remember
screwing up.</b></Default>

c0000052
00:02:43.040 --> 00:02:46.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, if the Masked Lord
is on the hunt for that witch.</b></Default>

c0000053
00:02:47.000 --> 00:02:48.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I guess this
is the safest place to be.</b></Default>

c0000054
00:02:49.000 --> 00:02:50.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
Yeah, and for all we know,</b></Default>

c0000055
00:02:50.420 --> 00:02:52.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>she may have
already fled the nation.</b></Default>

c0000056
00:02:52.720 --> 00:02:54.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[JHIN]
We can only hope.</b></Default>

c0000057
00:02:54.590 --> 00:02:55.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm?</b></Default>

c0000058
00:02:55.680 --> 00:02:57.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, why isn't
the boss back yet?</b></Default>

c0000059
00:02:57.100 --> 00:02:59.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm?
Oh, I can go find her!</b></Default>

c0000060
00:02:59.720 --> 00:03:00.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[NENE]
I think I know where she is,</b></Default>

c0000061
00:03:00.930 --> 00:03:02.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>so it shouldn't take long.</b></Default>

c0000062
00:03:02.390 --> 00:03:05.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>See you later!
I'll be back!</b></Default>

c0000063
00:03:05.140 --> 00:03:06.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MILLAVAIR] You are the one
who leaked the intel</b></Default>

c0000064
00:03:06.770 --> 00:03:09.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that divulged
Sisbell's location.</b></Default>

c0000065
00:03:09.110 --> 00:03:10.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is that right?</b></Default>

c0000066
00:03:10.730 --> 00:03:12.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Speak now, and be honest.</b></Default>

c0000067
00:03:12.940 --> 00:03:15.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are you the real Elletear,
or a fraud?</b></Default>

c0000068
00:03:15.910 --> 00:03:17.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[laughs]</b></Default>

c0000069
00:03:18.410 --> 00:03:21.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You can't be serious,
Your Majesty, is this a joke?</b></Default>

c0000070
00:03:21.910 --> 00:03:23.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's no need
to look that solemn</b></Default>

c0000071
00:03:23.700 --> 00:03:25.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>when you're saying
something so funny.</b></Default>

c0000072
00:03:25.960 --> 00:03:29.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sisbell was carrying out
a highly classified assignment.</b></Default>

c0000073
00:03:29.380 --> 00:03:31.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MILLAVAIR] I was acting under
the suspicion that Alsamira</b></Default>

c0000074
00:03:31.670 --> 00:03:33.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>had connections
with the Empire.</b></Default>

c0000075
00:03:33.670 --> 00:03:36.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And somehow, the Zoa were aware
of the plan the next day.</b></Default>

c0000076
00:03:36.970 --> 00:03:38.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[smirks]</b></Default>

c0000077
00:03:38.140 --> 00:03:39.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The royal families
of the Sovereignty</b></Default>

c0000078
00:03:39.890 --> 00:03:42.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>are not without
our domestic conflicts.</b></Default>

c0000079
00:03:42.720 --> 00:03:45.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All three factions
competing for one throne,</b></Default>

c0000080
00:03:45.180 --> 00:03:46.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>what could go wrong?</b></Default>

c0000081
00:03:46.480 --> 00:03:49.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So you understand the dynamics
of the three families?</b></Default>

c0000082
00:03:49.520 --> 00:03:50.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes, of course.</b></Default>

c0000083
00:03:50.940 --> 00:03:54.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The Lou are pacifists, wishing
to avoid bloody conflict</b></Default>

c0000084
00:03:54.280 --> 00:03:55.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with the Empire.</b></Default>

c0000085
00:03:55.740 --> 00:03:57.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Like witches of the same coven,
the Hydra have acted</b></Default>

c0000086
00:03:58.070 --> 00:03:59.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>as loyal advisers
and supporters</b></Default>

c0000087
00:03:59.990 --> 00:04:01.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of the Queen's campaign.</b></Default>

c0000088
00:04:02.030 --> 00:04:03.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But the Zoa, they're different.</b></Default>

c0000089
00:04:04.040 --> 00:04:07.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ruthless extremists who wish
to destroy the Empire,</b></Default>

c0000090
00:04:07.120 --> 00:04:08.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>no matter the cost.</b></Default>

c0000091
00:04:08.750 --> 00:04:10.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The relationship
between Zoa and Lou</b></Default>

c0000092
00:04:10.630 --> 00:04:12.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is one fraught
with tribulation.</b></Default>

c0000093
00:04:12.920 --> 00:04:15.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MILLAVAIR] If you are indeed
the real Elletear,</b></Default>

c0000094
00:04:15.130 --> 00:04:19.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you would never be complicit in
revealing Sisbell's location.</b></Default>

c0000095
00:04:19.380 --> 00:04:21.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[laughs]</b></Default>

c0000096
00:04:21.340 --> 00:04:24.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ELLETEAR] [laughing]
I can't do it.</b></Default>

c0000097
00:04:24.720 --> 00:04:27.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is too much,
Your Majesty, or should I say.</b></Default>

c0000098
00:04:27.850 --> 00:04:31.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My majesty's imposter,
whoever you are.</b></Default>

c0000099
00:04:32.270 --> 00:04:34.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What an impressive recreation.</b></Default>

c0000100
00:04:34.940 --> 00:04:36.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You may have been
able to fool Alice.</b></Default>

c0000101
00:04:37.030 --> 00:04:39.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hell, Sisbell would've
fallen for it too.</b></Default>

c0000102
00:04:39.910 --> 00:04:42.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please, dear,
haven't we danced enough?</b></Default>

c0000103
00:04:43.080 --> 00:04:44.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000104
00:04:44.990 --> 00:04:48.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How? How were you
able to tell it wasn't her?</b></Default>

c0000105
00:04:48.290 --> 00:04:51.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We astral power wielders
recognize our own.</b></Default>

c0000106
00:04:51.670 --> 00:04:54.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Although.
Your grasp is far superior.</b></Default>

c0000107
00:04:54.670 --> 00:04:57.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-It's not!
-I'm quite envious.</b></Default>

c0000108
00:04:57.630 --> 00:04:58.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000109
00:04:58.720 --> 00:05:01.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Easy, now, the girl was
acting under my orders.</b></Default>

c0000110
00:05:01.720 --> 00:05:03.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please do try to forgive her.</b></Default>

c0000111
00:05:03.350 --> 00:05:04.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[giggles]</b></Default>

c0000112
00:05:04.470 --> 00:05:06.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do not fret,
I had a lovely time.</b></Default>

c0000113
00:05:07.390 --> 00:05:09.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We're on watch,
I had to make sure</b></Default>

c0000114
00:05:09.100 --> 00:05:10.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it was the real you.</b></Default>

c0000115
00:05:10.440 --> 00:05:12.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I knew you would see
through the façade.</b></Default>

c0000116
00:05:14.610 --> 00:05:16.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIN]
Lady Alice, slow down!</b></Default>

c0000117
00:05:16.480 --> 00:05:18.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Running through this hall
is strictly forbidden!</b></Default>

c0000118
00:05:18.650 --> 00:05:20.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE] Hands off,
this is an emergency!</b></Default>

c0000119
00:05:21.160 --> 00:05:23.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your Majesty!
It's Sisbell!</b></Default>

c0000120
00:05:23.490 --> 00:05:24.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I must speak to you at once!</b></Default>

c0000121
00:05:25.870 --> 00:05:27.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MISMIS]
Ah,</b></Default>

c0000122
00:05:27.290 --> 00:05:29.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>this is the life.</b></Default>

c0000123
00:05:29.450 --> 00:05:31.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I knew you'd be here.</b></Default>

c0000124
00:05:31.080 --> 00:05:32.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[NENE]
What about your training?</b></Default>

c0000125
00:05:32.170 --> 00:05:33.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, hey, Nene!</b></Default>

c0000126
00:05:33.500 --> 00:05:35.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm already finished with that.</b></Default>

c0000127
00:05:35.500 --> 00:05:37.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I worked up a mean sweat
at the gym.</b></Default>

c0000128
00:05:37.710 --> 00:05:39.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And then, I took an
extended dip in the pool, so...</b></Default>

c0000129
00:05:39.880 --> 00:05:40.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Captain.
-Huh?</b></Default>

c0000130
00:05:40.970 --> 00:05:42.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-I can see your bits.
-[screams]</b></Default>

c0000131
00:05:42.760 --> 00:05:44.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't feel too bad about it.</b></Default>

c0000132
00:05:44.220 --> 00:05:47.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Where I come from, we call
people like you exhibitionists.</b></Default>

c0000133
00:05:47.310 --> 00:05:48.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SISBELL]
She's exactly right.</b></Default>

c0000134
00:05:48.850 --> 00:05:51.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[both gasp]
-You're fully exposed.</b></Default>

c0000135
00:05:51.690 --> 00:05:54.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And I mean, everything.</b></Default>

c0000136
00:05:54.230 --> 00:05:55.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll show you.</b></Default>

c0000137
00:05:55.770 --> 00:05:57.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[both gasping]</b></Default>

c0000138
00:05:57.770 --> 00:05:59.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Come on!
What was that?</b></Default>

c0000139
00:05:59.530 --> 00:06:01.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, I'm so sorry.</b></Default>

c0000140
00:06:01.110 --> 00:06:02.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Luckily, for you two</b></Default>

c0000141
00:06:02.400 --> 00:06:04.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I may have brought
just the thing.</b></Default>

c0000142
00:06:04.320 --> 00:06:06.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The bandages made
in the Empire are limited.</b></Default>

c0000143
00:06:06.830 --> 00:06:07.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They do work.</b></Default>

c0000144
00:06:07.910 --> 00:06:09.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but they don't hide
the astral energy</b></Default>

c0000145
00:06:09.330 --> 00:06:11.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that's invisible
to the naked eye.</b></Default>

c0000146
00:06:11.250 --> 00:06:12.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SISBELL]
May I?</b></Default>

c0000147
00:06:12.540 --> 00:06:14.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000148
00:06:16.250 --> 00:06:18.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey! Wait!</b></Default>

c0000149
00:06:18.420 --> 00:06:19.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm.</b></Default>

c0000150
00:06:19.880 --> 00:06:21.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I shall wait
for you in the cafe.</b></Default>

c0000151
00:06:22.470 --> 00:06:24.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What's Elletear doing here?</b></Default>

c0000152
00:06:24.630 --> 00:06:27.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I suspect it'd be difficult
to talk about Sisbell</b></Default>

c0000153
00:06:27.640 --> 00:06:28.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with me in the room.</b></Default>

c0000154
00:06:28.810 --> 00:06:31.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>After all,
I am a "suspect," aren't I?</b></Default>

c0000155
00:06:31.310 --> 00:06:33.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm.
Please excuse me, Your Majesty.</b></Default>

c0000156
00:06:34.060 --> 00:06:35.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000157
00:06:38.270 --> 00:06:39.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ah?</b></Default>

c0000158
00:06:41.360 --> 00:06:43.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MILLAVAIR]
Alice? What's wrong, dear?</b></Default>

c0000159
00:06:44.740 --> 00:06:46.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE] I have a letter
that's addressed to you.</b></Default>

c0000160
00:06:49.740 --> 00:06:52.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We're in a bit
of a predicament here.</b></Default>

c0000161
00:06:52.160 --> 00:06:54.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It seems Sisbell has been
accused of having connections</b></Default>

c0000162
00:06:54.830 --> 00:06:55.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with the Empire.</b></Default>

c0000163
00:06:55.960 --> 00:06:57.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MILLAVAIR]
By Masked Lord, of all people.</b></Default>

c0000164
00:06:57.960 --> 00:06:59.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Correct.</b></Default>

c0000165
00:06:59.750 --> 00:07:02.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is the perfect opportunity
for the House of Zoa</b></Default>

c0000166
00:07:02.260 --> 00:07:03.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to win the election.</b></Default>

c0000167
00:07:03.840 --> 00:07:05.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Regardless, why hasn't Sisbell</b></Default>

c0000168
00:07:05.930 --> 00:07:07.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>returned to the
Sovereignty yet?</b></Default>

c0000169
00:07:07.930 --> 00:07:09.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She's taking
another route home,</b></Default>

c0000170
00:07:09.350 --> 00:07:10.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and we thought
it would be unwise</b></Default>

c0000171
00:07:10.600 --> 00:07:12.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to travel together,
My Lady, so...</b></Default>

c0000172
00:07:12.890 --> 00:07:15.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I shall send royal guards.</b></Default>

c0000173
00:07:15.100 --> 00:07:17.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This letter, it mentions
something of note.</b></Default>

c0000174
00:07:17.690 --> 00:07:19.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It says that Sisbell met
the Imperial soldier</b></Default>

c0000175
00:07:19.940 --> 00:07:23.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>who saved her a year ago,
at Alsamira.</b></Default>

c0000176
00:07:23.240 --> 00:07:24.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MILLAVAIR]
Alice, you don't happen to know</b></Default>

c0000177
00:07:24.780 --> 00:07:26.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>anything about this person,
do you?</b></Default>

c0000178
00:07:26.910 --> 00:07:29.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-No, I do not.
-[groans]</b></Default>

c0000179
00:07:29.160 --> 00:07:31.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He wasn't in Alsamira,
or the battlefield,</b></Default>

c0000180
00:07:31.530 --> 00:07:33.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>or in any neutral cities.</b></Default>

c0000181
00:07:33.700 --> 00:07:36.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't know, Rin, is there
anywhere else I forgot?</b></Default>

c0000182
00:07:36.500 --> 00:07:38.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIN] It's probably best
you forget how to speak.</b></Default>

c0000183
00:07:38.750 --> 00:07:40.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What I'm trying to say,</b></Default>

c0000184
00:07:40.420 --> 00:07:42.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is I don't know a damn thing,
Your Majesty!</b></Default>

c0000185
00:07:43.050 --> 00:07:45.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How could I know
anything about Iska?</b></Default>

c0000186
00:07:45.340 --> 00:07:47.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He is Imperial, after all.</b></Default>

c0000187
00:07:47.800 --> 00:07:49.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes, right away, ma'am.</b></Default>

c0000188
00:07:50.010 --> 00:07:52.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I appreciate your willingness
to meet with me.</b></Default>

c0000189
00:07:53.020 --> 00:07:54.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SISBELL]
Captain Mismis,</b></Default>

c0000190
00:07:54.470 --> 00:07:56.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Iska, Nene.</b></Default>

c0000191
00:07:56.980 --> 00:07:58.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And you too, Jhin.</b></Default>

c0000192
00:07:58.190 --> 00:08:00.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, good job
knowing our names.</b></Default>

c0000193
00:08:00.190 --> 00:08:01.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What do you want from us?</b></Default>

c0000194
00:08:01.690 --> 00:08:03.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wouldn't you like
to sit down first?</b></Default>

c0000195
00:08:03.360 --> 00:08:05.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[JHIN]
Where would you prefer I sit?</b></Default>

c0000196
00:08:05.280 --> 00:08:06.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SISBELL]
Right here.</b></Default>

c0000197
00:08:06.360 --> 00:08:09.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Unless you are afraid to do so,
I am a witch.</b></Default>

c0000198
00:08:09.490 --> 00:08:10.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll sit wherever
it pleases you,</b></Default>

c0000199
00:08:11.080 --> 00:08:12.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if you have some useful info.</b></Default>

c0000200
00:08:12.740 --> 00:08:13.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Tell us what you want first.</b></Default>

c0000201
00:08:14.080 --> 00:08:15.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh, ma'am, sorry.</b></Default>

c0000202
00:08:15.450 --> 00:08:17.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I thought you'd be far away
from here by now.</b></Default>

c0000203
00:08:17.830 --> 00:08:20.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll leave,
I plan on returning home soon.</b></Default>

c0000204
00:08:21.580 --> 00:08:23.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Along with all of you.
'Kay?</b></Default>

c0000205
00:08:23.500 --> 00:08:24.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[all gasping]</b></Default>

c0000206
00:08:24.840 --> 00:08:26.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Huh?
-Wait, what?</b></Default>

c0000207
00:08:26.420 --> 00:08:28.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I would like for you three
to escort me.</b></Default>

c0000208
00:08:28.430 --> 00:08:30.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You'll be my hired guards,</b></Default>

c0000209
00:08:30.180 --> 00:08:33.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to defend me from astral
power forces on the trip home.</b></Default>

c0000210
00:08:33.310 --> 00:08:34.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-What?!
-What?!</b></Default>

c0000211
00:08:35.180 --> 00:08:36.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[JHIN]
No freakin' way.</b></Default>

c0000212
00:08:36.520 --> 00:08:37.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If the command center finds out</b></Default>

c0000213
00:08:37.810 --> 00:08:39.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we're protecting
the Sovereignty,</b></Default>

c0000214
00:08:39.310 --> 00:08:40.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>we might as well retire.</b></Default>

c0000215
00:08:40.560 --> 00:08:41.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Nice try.
-[JHIN] What?</b></Default>

c0000216
00:08:41.980 --> 00:08:43.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The truth is you don't
want them to find out</b></Default>

c0000217
00:08:43.690 --> 00:08:45.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Captain Mismis here is a witch.</b></Default>

c0000218
00:08:46.400 --> 00:08:48.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-You know about that?
-[SISBELL] Yes.</b></Default>

c0000219
00:08:49.740 --> 00:08:52.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This rare material
is called nebula.</b></Default>

c0000220
00:08:52.450 --> 00:08:55.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The Empire doesn't have
anything even close to this.</b></Default>

c0000221
00:08:55.370 --> 00:08:57.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It can hide astral energy.</b></Default>

c0000222
00:08:58.000 --> 00:08:59.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Whoa.</b></Default>

c0000223
00:08:59.210 --> 00:09:00.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SISBELL]
If you agree to protect me</b></Default>

c0000224
00:09:00.500 --> 00:09:02.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>on my return
to the Sovereignty,</b></Default>

c0000225
00:09:02.130 --> 00:09:04.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>this bandage is yours.</b></Default>

c0000226
00:09:04.090 --> 00:09:06.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm not asking you to betray
the Empire for me.</b></Default>

c0000227
00:09:07.880 --> 00:09:09.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My enemies are from my nation.</b></Default>

c0000228
00:09:09.800 --> 00:09:12.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They are astral mages
from my home.</b></Default>

c0000229
00:09:12.180 --> 00:09:14.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, it's only natural
for Imperial forces</b></Default>

c0000230
00:09:14.260 --> 00:09:15.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to fight against them.</b></Default>

c0000231
00:09:15.680 --> 00:09:18.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Isn't that right, Captain?
-I, uh... I can't answer that.</b></Default>

c0000232
00:09:18.770 --> 00:09:20.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Fine, we're in.
-Okay, that's enough.</b></Default>

c0000233
00:09:20.690 --> 00:09:23.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA] If that's what it takes,
you have a deal, Sisbell.</b></Default>

c0000234
00:09:23.360 --> 00:09:25.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Iska? Nene?
Stand down!</b></Default>

c0000235
00:09:25.650 --> 00:09:27.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We are all in agreement.</b></Default>

c0000236
00:09:27.820 --> 00:09:30.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I know you couldn't approve
a mission to protect the enemy.</b></Default>

c0000237
00:09:30.950 --> 00:09:33.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, there's no need to worry,
we chose this on our own!</b></Default>

c0000238
00:09:33.870 --> 00:09:36.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We won't do anything
to the detriment of the Empire.</b></Default>

c0000239
00:09:36.870 --> 00:09:39.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[JHIN] We'll only fight back
if the astral mages attack.</b></Default>

c0000240
00:09:39.870 --> 00:09:42.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If the Imperial army
decides to come after you,</b></Default>

c0000241
00:09:42.370 --> 00:09:43.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you're on your own.</b></Default>

c0000242
00:09:43.580 --> 00:09:45.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'd expect no less.</b></Default>

c0000243
00:09:45.340 --> 00:09:47.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is just
a business transaction.</b></Default>

c0000244
00:09:47.840 --> 00:09:50.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We'll protect you
for 30 days, tops.</b></Default>

c0000245
00:09:50.170 --> 00:09:52.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Sound good?
-[SISBELL] Yes, it does.</b></Default>

c0000246
00:09:52.840 --> 00:09:54.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've got one last
question, though.</b></Default>

c0000247
00:09:54.840 --> 00:09:57.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why are they after you, anyway?</b></Default>

c0000248
00:09:57.560 --> 00:09:59.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

c0000249
00:09:59.560 --> 00:10:01.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If I don't return
to the Queen's Palace,</b></Default>

c0000250
00:10:01.850 --> 00:10:03.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>then full-scale war breaks out</b></Default>

c0000251
00:10:03.350 --> 00:10:05.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>between the Sovereignty
and the Empire.</b></Default>

c0000252
00:10:05.270 --> 00:10:06.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Full-scale--</b></Default>

c0000253
00:10:06.440 --> 00:10:08.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The conflict would end
with the total annihilation</b></Default>

c0000254
00:10:08.780 --> 00:10:09.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of the planet.</b></Default>

c0000255
00:10:09.900 --> 00:10:12.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Which is why I must
return home, at once.</b></Default>

c0000256
00:10:12.320 --> 00:10:13.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But how can you be so sure?</b></Default>

c0000257
00:10:14.030 --> 00:10:15.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I am a retainer for the Queen.</b></Default>

c0000258
00:10:16.740 --> 00:10:19.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Someone seeks to overthrow
the current regime.</b></Default>

c0000259
00:10:19.660 --> 00:10:22.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SISBELL] Their goal is to
start a war with the Empire.</b></Default>

c0000260
00:10:22.250 --> 00:10:24.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is it Lord Mask?</b></Default>

c0000261
00:10:24.460 --> 00:10:26.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SISBELL]
He is one of the suspects, yes.</b></Default>

c0000262
00:10:26.960 --> 00:10:28.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm on a special mission.</b></Default>

c0000263
00:10:28.800 --> 00:10:30.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My goal is to find the traitor.</b></Default>

c0000264
00:10:30.840 --> 00:10:33.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's why all these
mages are after me.</b></Default>

c0000265
00:10:33.550 --> 00:10:36.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Allow me to take care
of the bill tonight.</b></Default>

c0000266
00:10:36.220 --> 00:10:39.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please consider this
a token of our friendship.</b></Default>

c0000267
00:10:39.100 --> 00:10:41.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're the only person
that ordered anything.</b></Default>

c0000268
00:10:41.560 --> 00:10:44.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Shall we head out, then?
-Did you hear what I said?</b></Default>

c0000269
00:10:44.890 --> 00:10:46.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIN] Lady Alice, should you
really be lounging around</b></Default>

c0000270
00:10:46.900 --> 00:10:48.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in here like this?</b></Default>

c0000271
00:10:48.230 --> 00:10:50.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What's the issue?
I'm on a bed.</b></Default>

c0000272
00:10:50.110 --> 00:10:52.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIN] The issue is that
this bed happens to be</b></Default>

c0000273
00:10:52.320 --> 00:10:53.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in Lady Sisbell's room.</b></Default>

c0000274
00:10:53.990 --> 00:10:55.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can't help but wonder
what Sisbell might be</b></Default>

c0000275
00:10:55.990 --> 00:10:57.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>doing right now.</b></Default>

c0000276
00:10:57.450 --> 00:10:59.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIN]
We will know soon enough.</b></Default>

c0000277
00:10:59.120 --> 00:11:00.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your Majesty's guards
are on their way</b></Default>

c0000278
00:11:00.660 --> 00:11:02.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to provide protection.</b></Default>

c0000279
00:11:02.250 --> 00:11:03.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

c0000280
00:11:03.540 --> 00:11:04.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are you baiting me?</b></Default>

c0000281
00:11:04.830 --> 00:11:06.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Fine, then, I shall
take the bait.</b></Default>

c0000282
00:11:06.420 --> 00:11:08.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What is that big sigh about?</b></Default>

c0000283
00:11:08.130 --> 00:11:10.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The question is,
what's not to sigh about?</b></Default>

c0000284
00:11:10.840 --> 00:11:13.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All these dumb, formal meetings
that I am forced to attend,</b></Default>

c0000285
00:11:13.630 --> 00:11:16.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>big-sisterly worry over
my errant younger sibling,</b></Default>

c0000286
00:11:16.720 --> 00:11:19.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and the matter with Elletear
weighs on my mind, as well.</b></Default>

c0000287
00:11:19.930 --> 00:11:22.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Seems like I hardly have time
for my own thoughts these days.</b></Default>

c0000288
00:11:23.020 --> 00:11:25.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You do skip many
of those meetings, though.</b></Default>

c0000289
00:11:25.770 --> 00:11:28.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[grunts]
-Forgive my insolence.</b></Default>

c0000290
00:11:28.190 --> 00:11:30.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Never mind that I have
to fight the Saint Disciples,</b></Default>

c0000291
00:11:30.570 --> 00:11:31.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>protect the Sovereignty.</b></Default>

c0000292
00:11:31.690 --> 00:11:32.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll have to fight
the strongest</b></Default>

c0000293
00:11:32.860 --> 00:11:34.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>ex-Saint Disciple swordsman,
too, no doubt,</b></Default>

c0000294
00:11:34.940 --> 00:11:36.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and what about the times
when I'd fight with him</b></Default>

c0000295
00:11:36.530 --> 00:11:38.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in other ways, then we'd go
to the opera, eat pasta,</b></Default>

c0000296
00:11:38.780 --> 00:11:40.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and gallivant around like we're
best friends, it's too much--</b></Default>

c0000297
00:11:40.450 --> 00:11:42.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIN] I have to say it,
you keep talking about</b></Default>

c0000298
00:11:42.240 --> 00:11:43.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that one swordsman.</b></Default>

c0000299
00:11:43.330 --> 00:11:45.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]
Oh, come off it!</b></Default>

c0000300
00:11:45.370 --> 00:11:48.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE] Iska is my enemy,
and I speak of him as such!</b></Default>

c0000301
00:11:48.500 --> 00:11:51.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I shall not show mercy when
we meet on the battlefield!</b></Default>

c0000302
00:11:51.130 --> 00:11:52.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I am glad to hear it,
Lady Alice.</b></Default>

c0000303
00:11:52.920 --> 00:11:55.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE] Iska and I have
no choice but to fight!</b></Default>

c0000304
00:11:55.420 --> 00:11:56.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sisbell has some nerve to say</b></Default>

c0000305
00:11:56.760 --> 00:11:58.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>he's her "knight
in shining armor..."</b></Default>

c0000306
00:11:58.510 --> 00:11:59.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wait a minute!</b></Default>

c0000307
00:11:59.930 --> 00:12:01.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You don't think...</b></Default>

c0000308
00:12:01.140 --> 00:12:03.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No, she can't be
with Iska right now.</b></Default>

c0000309
00:12:03.270 --> 00:12:05.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-I will not stand for that!
-[RIN] Lady Alice,</b></Default>

c0000310
00:12:05.390 --> 00:12:06.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>please pull yourself together!</b></Default>

c0000311
00:12:07.600 --> 00:12:08.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[wind howling]</b></Default>

c0000312
00:12:08.940 --> 00:12:11.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Listen up,
we must remain on high alert.</b></Default>

c0000313
00:12:11.900 --> 00:12:14.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Who knows where Masked Lord's
assassins might be hiding?</b></Default>

c0000314
00:12:15.070 --> 00:12:17.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You are sitting
way too close to Iska!</b></Default>

c0000315
00:12:17.200 --> 00:12:18.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
Ahh.</b></Default>

c0000316
00:12:18.280 --> 00:12:20.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ah, but fate
has brought us together.</b></Default>

c0000317
00:12:20.450 --> 00:12:22.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I feel our dynamic
makes for a good</b></Default>

c0000318
00:12:22.200 --> 00:12:24.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>master-servant relationship.</b></Default>

c0000319
00:12:24.740 --> 00:12:26.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm sorry?
What are you on about?</b></Default>

c0000320
00:12:26.790 --> 00:12:29.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't forget
Iska is my subordinate!</b></Default>

c0000321
00:12:29.330 --> 00:12:32.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Just a bodyguard.
-Oh, yes, that's correct.</b></Default>

c0000322
00:12:32.340 --> 00:12:34.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I do apologize.</b></Default>

c0000323
00:12:34.710 --> 00:12:36.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And anyway, Iska is my friend!</b></Default>

c0000324
00:12:36.970 --> 00:12:38.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You can't have him all for
yourself, share him!</b></Default>

c0000325
00:12:38.840 --> 00:12:40.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You both forget
that I am not one of you.</b></Default>

c0000326
00:12:41.010 --> 00:12:42.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[both growling]</b></Default>

c0000327
00:12:42.600 --> 00:12:43.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You've no clue...</b></Default>

c0000328
00:12:44.760 --> 00:12:46.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>how reassuring this is.</b></Default>

c0000329
00:12:47.020 --> 00:12:49.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All I've had is Schwartz.
I just feel so relieved.</b></Default>

c0000330
00:12:50.060 --> 00:12:51.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[both sighing]</b></Default>

c0000331
00:12:51.400 --> 00:12:53.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

c0000332
00:12:53.110 --> 00:12:55.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Fine, have him,
but just this once!</b></Default>

c0000333
00:12:55.360 --> 00:12:57.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I guess it can't be helped.</b></Default>

c0000334
00:12:57.570 --> 00:13:00.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sisbell,
I just want to be clear.</b></Default>

c0000335
00:13:00.450 --> 00:13:02.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Once this guard detail ends,
so does our relationship.</b></Default>

c0000336
00:13:04.410 --> 00:13:05.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA] We'll be enemies
on the battlefield.</b></Default>

c0000337
00:13:05.990 --> 00:13:07.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You understand this, right?</b></Default>

c0000338
00:13:08.660 --> 00:13:10.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SISBELL]
Of course.</b></Default>

c0000339
00:13:10.500 --> 00:13:14.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Even if just during
the escort, I appreciate it.</b></Default>

c0000340
00:13:15.290 --> 00:13:17.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I am so grateful you're here.</b></Default>

c0000341
00:13:17.550 --> 00:13:19.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I hope you can feel it.</b></Default>

c0000342
00:13:20.630 --> 00:13:21.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[car revving]</b></Default>

c0000343
00:13:21.510 --> 00:13:24.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We'll be heading
to the Sovereignty indirectly.</b></Default>

c0000344
00:13:24.350 --> 00:13:26.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's necessary,
if we're to have any hope</b></Default>

c0000345
00:13:26.180 --> 00:13:28.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of avoiding Zoa's detection.</b></Default>

c0000346
00:13:28.140 --> 00:13:30.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>As such, I recommend
that we spend the night here.</b></Default>

c0000347
00:13:30.980 --> 00:13:32.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A very wise choice, Schwartz.</b></Default>

c0000348
00:13:32.900 --> 00:13:35.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Also, I am simply famished.</b></Default>

c0000349
00:13:35.650 --> 00:13:37.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Iska!</b></Default>

c0000350
00:13:37.820 --> 00:13:40.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We have so many restaurants
to choose from!</b></Default>

c0000351
00:13:40.190 --> 00:13:41.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SISBELL]
Where would you like to eat?</b></Default>

c0000352
00:13:41.490 --> 00:13:42.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000353
00:13:42.740 --> 00:13:44.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We're your guards, aren't we?</b></Default>

c0000354
00:13:44.490 --> 00:13:46.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, we'll go
wherever you decide to eat.</b></Default>

c0000355
00:13:46.620 --> 00:13:47.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And another thing...</b></Default>

c0000356
00:13:47.910 --> 00:13:49.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>since you seem
to be feeling better,</b></Default>

c0000357
00:13:49.500 --> 00:13:51.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>could you let go of my arm?</b></Default>

c0000358
00:13:51.540 --> 00:13:52.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, of course.</b></Default>

c0000359
00:13:52.790 --> 00:13:54.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[giggles]
But let's hug, instead!</b></Default>

c0000360
00:13:54.250 --> 00:13:55.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TOGETHER] It's just a mission,
it's just a mission</b></Default>

c0000361
00:13:55.540 --> 00:13:56.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it's just a mission,
it's just a mission.</b></Default>

c0000362
00:13:56.840 --> 00:13:57.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's just a mission,
it's just a mission</b></Default>

c0000363
00:13:58.000 --> 00:14:01.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You two aren't disguising
your murderous intent.</b></Default>

c0000364
00:14:01.090 --> 00:14:02.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have an idea, Iska.</b></Default>

c0000365
00:14:02.590 --> 00:14:05.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I want you to try and guess
my absolute favorite food.</b></Default>

c0000366
00:14:05.510 --> 00:14:07.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And that is what we all
shall have for dinner tonight.</b></Default>

c0000367
00:14:07.970 --> 00:14:08.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your favorite?</b></Default>

c0000368
00:14:09.060 --> 00:14:11.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SISBELL] [giggles]
Are you stumped?</b></Default>

c0000369
00:14:11.180 --> 00:14:13.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If it's too hard, I can make it
a multiple choice...</b></Default>

c0000370
00:14:13.140 --> 00:14:15.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Pasta.
-[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000371
00:14:15.520 --> 00:14:18.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And that's right!
How did you possibly guess?</b></Default>

c0000372
00:14:18.570 --> 00:14:20.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A hunch.</b></Default>

c0000373
00:14:20.570 --> 00:14:22.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[giggles]</b></Default>

c0000374
00:14:22.700 --> 00:14:25.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
These two. Sisters for sure.</b></Default>

c0000375
00:14:25.200 --> 00:14:26.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000376
00:14:26.950 --> 00:14:28.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wonder how she is.</b></Default>

c0000377
00:14:28.410 --> 00:14:29.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000378
00:14:29.870 --> 00:14:31.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Alice.</b></Default>

c0000379
00:14:31.750 --> 00:14:33.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE] Maybe I should've
dragged her back here with me</b></Default>

c0000380
00:14:33.870 --> 00:14:35.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>against her will.</b></Default>

c0000381
00:14:35.250 --> 00:14:37.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIN]
Lady Alice,</b></Default>

c0000382
00:14:37.130 --> 00:14:39.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I apologize
for disturbing you so late.</b></Default>

c0000383
00:14:39.130 --> 00:14:41.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Is something wrong?
-You have a guest here.</b></Default>

c0000384
00:14:41.960 --> 00:14:43.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Would you like for me
to send him away?</b></Default>

c0000385
00:14:43.970 --> 00:14:45.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes, of course.</b></Default>

c0000386
00:14:45.220 --> 00:14:47.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How rude to come at this hour.</b></Default>

c0000387
00:14:47.930 --> 00:14:50.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
Tell me. Who is it?</b></Default>

c0000388
00:14:50.390 --> 00:14:51.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIN]
It's Masked Lord.</b></Default>

c0000389
00:14:51.810 --> 00:14:53.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ON (MASKED LORD)]
Apologies.</b></Default>

c0000390
00:14:53.350 --> 00:14:54.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm aware
how uncouth it is of me</b></Default>

c0000391
00:14:55.140 --> 00:14:58.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to call upon you
at such an uncivilized hour.</b></Default>

c0000392
00:14:58.690 --> 00:15:01.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's fine.
So what brings you here?</b></Default>

c0000393
00:15:01.320 --> 00:15:03.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Have you heard the talk?</b></Default>

c0000394
00:15:03.110 --> 00:15:06.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Lady Sisbell may have forged
connections with the Empire?</b></Default>

c0000395
00:15:06.240 --> 00:15:08.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Surely, you have.
-We've not.</b></Default>

c0000396
00:15:08.530 --> 00:15:11.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If she is indeed working
with an Imperial soldier,</b></Default>

c0000397
00:15:11.450 --> 00:15:13.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that would equal treason.</b></Default>

c0000398
00:15:13.790 --> 00:15:15.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ON (MASKED LORD)] It would
mean the Queen's downfall,</b></Default>

c0000399
00:15:15.790 --> 00:15:17.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and yours, too, as a princess.</b></Default>

c0000400
00:15:18.000 --> 00:15:20.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sisbell cannot be
connected to the Empire.</b></Default>

c0000401
00:15:20.170 --> 00:15:21.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They're just rumors.</b></Default>

c0000402
00:15:21.670 --> 00:15:23.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[smirks]
Oh?</b></Default>

c0000403
00:15:23.260 --> 00:15:26.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then you won't object
to investigating it together?</b></Default>

c0000404
00:15:26.220 --> 00:15:28.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Letting the results
speak for themselves?</b></Default>

c0000405
00:15:28.510 --> 00:15:30.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[smirks]</b></Default>

c0000406
00:15:30.470 --> 00:15:32.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No objections here.</b></Default>

c0000407
00:15:32.850 --> 00:15:35.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Phew,
we made into the Sovereignty.</b></Default>

c0000408
00:15:35.810 --> 00:15:36.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

c0000409
00:15:36.900 --> 00:15:39.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>See?
Just as I promised.</b></Default>

c0000410
00:15:39.110 --> 00:15:41.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I told you there was nothing
to be worried about.</b></Default>

c0000411
00:15:41.530 --> 00:15:43.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm not sure
you ought to be so glad</b></Default>

c0000412
00:15:43.110 --> 00:15:45.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>your borders
are this easy to cross.</b></Default>

c0000413
00:15:45.360 --> 00:15:48.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA] And what if they
demanded an astral power trial?</b></Default>

c0000414
00:15:48.110 --> 00:15:50.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then I would have shouted
at them to leave us alone.</b></Default>

c0000415
00:15:50.700 --> 00:15:52.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Of course,
if they'd found us out,</b></Default>

c0000416
00:15:52.240 --> 00:15:53.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it would've been a nightmare.</b></Default>

c0000417
00:15:53.580 --> 00:15:55.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[awkward chuckle]</b></Default>

c0000418
00:15:55.370 --> 00:15:56.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And I'm desperate.</b></Default>

c0000419
00:15:56.670 --> 00:15:58.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've little choice.</b></Default>

c0000420
00:15:58.670 --> 00:16:01.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Our palace is a vipers' nest.</b></Default>

c0000421
00:16:01.170 --> 00:16:03.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I must protect the Queen.</b></Default>

c0000422
00:16:03.090 --> 00:16:04.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Vipers, huh?
-Mm, huh.</b></Default>

c0000423
00:16:04.380 --> 00:16:06.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm sorry,
I shouldn't have said that.</b></Default>

c0000424
00:16:08.130 --> 00:16:09.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm.</b></Default>

c0000425
00:16:09.340 --> 00:16:11.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SISBELL] What are you
thinking, Iska? Tell me.</b></Default>

c0000426
00:16:11.970 --> 00:16:12.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, it's nothing.</b></Default>

c0000427
00:16:13.060 --> 00:16:16.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I just noticed that cafes seem
to be the same in every nation.</b></Default>

c0000428
00:16:16.640 --> 00:16:19.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>100 years ago,
astral mages fled the Empire</b></Default>

c0000429
00:16:19.940 --> 00:16:21.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and founded a new nation.</b></Default>

c0000430
00:16:21.400 --> 00:16:23.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This, the Nebulis Sovereignty.</b></Default>

c0000431
00:16:23.690 --> 00:16:25.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SISBELL] We share the same
roots, and we always will.</b></Default>

c0000432
00:16:26.070 --> 00:16:27.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We've more in common than not.</b></Default>

c0000433
00:16:27.910 --> 00:16:29.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Our language and culture
are the same.</b></Default>

c0000434
00:16:29.990 --> 00:16:32.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The main difference
is that everyone in this city</b></Default>

c0000435
00:16:32.120 --> 00:16:33.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>is an astral mage.</b></Default>

c0000436
00:16:33.620 --> 00:16:35.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Every person that you see.</b></Default>

c0000437
00:16:35.450 --> 00:16:37.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
Even that girl in the cafe.</b></Default>

c0000438
00:16:37.210 --> 00:16:40.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She could be a formidable
astral mage powerful enough</b></Default>

c0000439
00:16:40.250 --> 00:16:42.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to subdue Imperial soldiers.</b></Default>

c0000440
00:16:42.500 --> 00:16:44.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA] That's why the Empire
persecuted them.</b></Default>

c0000441
00:16:44.760 --> 00:16:48.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Branded them as heretics,
"witches" and "demons."</b></Default>

c0000442
00:16:48.420 --> 00:16:50.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It was all done in fear.</b></Default>

c0000443
00:16:50.180 --> 00:16:52.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000444
00:16:54.140 --> 00:16:55.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Security seems tight here.</b></Default>

c0000445
00:16:55.770 --> 00:16:56.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you think that
they're on the lookout</b></Default>

c0000446
00:16:57.020 --> 00:16:58.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for Imperial soldiers?</b></Default>

c0000447
00:16:58.230 --> 00:16:59.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No, it's something else.</b></Default>

c0000448
00:16:59.940 --> 00:17:02.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's a province-wide
patrol detail</b></Default>

c0000449
00:17:02.230 --> 00:17:03.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to track down a criminal.</b></Default>

c0000450
00:17:03.610 --> 00:17:06.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They're out looking
for an escapee on the lam.</b></Default>

c0000451
00:17:06.150 --> 00:17:08.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, they have more than the
Imperial army to worry about.</b></Default>

c0000452
00:17:09.030 --> 00:17:10.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Some people in the Empire
misuse guns</b></Default>

c0000453
00:17:10.910 --> 00:17:12.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and other weapons, right?</b></Default>

c0000454
00:17:12.280 --> 00:17:15.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well, not all astral mages
are well-intentioned, you know.</b></Default>

c0000455
00:17:15.580 --> 00:17:17.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This criminal is the worst.</b></Default>

c0000456
00:17:17.540 --> 00:17:21.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He is extremely dangerous,
a demon named Salinger.</b></Default>

c0000457
00:17:21.370 --> 00:17:23.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What did you just say?</b></Default>

c0000458
00:17:23.750 --> 00:17:26.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000459
00:17:26.250 --> 00:17:28.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SISBELL]
Hello? Iska?</b></Default>

c0000460
00:17:28.170 --> 00:17:30.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Where did you go?
What just happened?</b></Default>

c0000461
00:17:30.760 --> 00:17:34.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A lot of things, but let's just
focus on the here and now,</b></Default>

c0000462
00:17:34.260 --> 00:17:36.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and getting you home.</b></Default>

c0000463
00:17:36.310 --> 00:17:38.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA] How do you propose
we reach the palace?</b></Default>

c0000464
00:17:38.310 --> 00:17:40.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The Central Province
seems so far away.</b></Default>

c0000465
00:17:40.430 --> 00:17:41.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Good question!</b></Default>

c0000466
00:17:41.730 --> 00:17:43.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is where the real
challenge begins!</b></Default>

c0000467
00:17:43.400 --> 00:17:44.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[water splashing]</b></Default>

c0000468
00:17:44.400 --> 00:17:46.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE] What?
You mean she's coming here?</b></Default>

c0000469
00:17:47.690 --> 00:17:49.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Thank you for the shower.</b></Default>

c0000470
00:17:49.150 --> 00:17:52.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-So then, where is Sisbell?
-On the move.</b></Default>

c0000471
00:17:52.200 --> 00:17:54.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She did pass
the border checkpoint,</b></Default>

c0000472
00:17:54.120 --> 00:17:56.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and entered
the Sovereignty today.</b></Default>

c0000473
00:17:56.280 --> 00:17:58.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE] Was it just the two
of them? Her and Schwartz?</b></Default>

c0000474
00:17:58.120 --> 00:17:59.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIN]
No, she's with four others</b></Default>

c0000475
00:17:59.580 --> 00:18:01.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>who are acting
as her bodyguards.</b></Default>

c0000476
00:18:01.410 --> 00:18:04.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She claims they're mercenaries
she hired in Alsamira.</b></Default>

c0000477
00:18:04.380 --> 00:18:05.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've nothing but admiration.</b></Default>

c0000478
00:18:06.000 --> 00:18:08.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are you telling me
that Sisbell hired them?</b></Default>

c0000479
00:18:08.420 --> 00:18:10.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000480
00:18:10.420 --> 00:18:13.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It is impressive,
Lady Alice, quite so, indeed.</b></Default>

c0000481
00:18:13.260 --> 00:18:15.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE] I'm sorry, what are
you talking about right now?</b></Default>

c0000482
00:18:15.930 --> 00:18:17.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIN]
Her Majesty wishes you</b></Default>

c0000483
00:18:17.180 --> 00:18:18.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to travel
to Riesbarten at once.</b></Default>

c0000484
00:18:19.060 --> 00:18:21.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In order to protect
Lady Sisbell.</b></Default>

c0000485
00:18:21.940 --> 00:18:23.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wait, just me?</b></Default>

c0000486
00:18:23.190 --> 00:18:25.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Surely Masked Lord
will tag along.</b></Default>

c0000487
00:18:25.440 --> 00:18:27.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIN] Her Majesty will hold
a Three-Founding-Family</b></Default>

c0000488
00:18:27.690 --> 00:18:29.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>conference tomorrow.</b></Default>

c0000489
00:18:29.280 --> 00:18:31.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>To keep Masked Lord
of the Zoa here.</b></Default>

c0000490
00:18:31.650 --> 00:18:35.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Aa-ha, and that will be
our chance to slip away, smart!</b></Default>

c0000491
00:18:35.820 --> 00:18:37.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, but, won't it
look suspicious</b></Default>

c0000492
00:18:37.780 --> 00:18:39.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>if I don't attend this meeting?</b></Default>

c0000493
00:18:39.660 --> 00:18:41.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Lady Elletear
can be there in your stead.</b></Default>

c0000494
00:18:42.040 --> 00:18:43.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Right as always.</b></Default>

c0000495
00:18:43.670 --> 00:18:45.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Honestly, I don't know
what that impudent brat</b></Default>

c0000496
00:18:45.670 --> 00:18:47.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>could possibly be thinking.</b></Default>

c0000497
00:18:47.420 --> 00:18:49.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Nonetheless,
she is still my sister.</b></Default>

c0000498
00:18:49.550 --> 00:18:51.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm bound to help her,
at all costs.</b></Default>

c0000499
00:18:53.300 --> 00:18:55.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SISBELL]
We've only just begun.</b></Default>

c0000500
00:18:55.340 --> 00:18:57.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is where
the real mind game starts.</b></Default>

c0000501
00:18:58.060 --> 00:18:59.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The moment
I crossed the border,</b></Default>

c0000502
00:19:00.020 --> 00:19:02.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>they were notified of my
presence in the Sovereignty.</b></Default>

c0000503
00:19:03.640 --> 00:19:07.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Elletear or Alice,
quite possibly both of them.</b></Default>

c0000504
00:19:07.270 --> 00:19:09.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They're traitors
connected to...</b></Default>

c0000505
00:19:09.110 --> 00:19:12.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and likely conspiring with...
the House of Zoa.</b></Default>

c0000506
00:19:12.490 --> 00:19:14.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Even worse,
it's highly probable</b></Default>

c0000507
00:19:14.740 --> 00:19:17.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that they've joined forces
with that monster.</b></Default>

c0000508
00:19:17.620 --> 00:19:20.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If I am captured,
I will be imprisoned,</b></Default>

c0000509
00:19:20.660 --> 00:19:22.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>or otherwise silenced.</b></Default>

c0000510
00:19:22.660 --> 00:19:24.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Mother is the only one
I can trust.</b></Default>

c0000511
00:19:25.660 --> 00:19:28.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That is why I needed him.
A protector.</b></Default>

c0000512
00:19:29.710 --> 00:19:31.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I would do anything...</b></Default>

c0000513
00:19:31.340 --> 00:19:33.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'd even resort
to seducing him...</b></Default>

c0000514
00:19:33.260 --> 00:19:35.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in the name
of protecting this nation.</b></Default>

c0000515
00:19:35.380 --> 00:19:37.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Even if he sees me
as nothing but a filthy witch.</b></Default>

c0000516
00:19:38.050 --> 00:19:41.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But truthfully, Mother,
there is a freedom in this.</b></Default>

c0000517
00:19:41.720 --> 00:19:43.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In throwing myself at someone.</b></Default>

c0000518
00:19:43.730 --> 00:19:45.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A sense of relief.</b></Default>

c0000519
00:19:48.650 --> 00:19:49.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>At this moment...</b></Default>

c0000520
00:19:51.730 --> 00:19:53.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it seems...</b></Default>

c0000521
00:19:53.820 --> 00:19:55.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>all I have is Iska.</b></Default>

c0000522
00:19:56.530 --> 00:19:58.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How wonderful would it be?</b></Default>

c0000523
00:19:59.070 --> 00:20:00.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If I could stay
with him forever?</b></Default>

c0000524
00:20:02.660 --> 00:20:04.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Astral spirits...</b></Default>

c0000525
00:20:04.660 --> 00:20:06.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I ask for your guidance.</b></Default>

c0000526
00:20:08.920 --> 00:20:10.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Where is your servant?</b></Default>

c0000527
00:20:10.630 --> 00:20:12.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It is still pretty early.</b></Default>

c0000528
00:20:13.050 --> 00:20:15.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SISBELL] He just left
for the Central Province.</b></Default>

c0000529
00:20:15.590 --> 00:20:17.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Schwartz's astral power
makes him well suited</b></Default>

c0000530
00:20:17.840 --> 00:20:19.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>for covert missions.</b></Default>

c0000531
00:20:19.550 --> 00:20:21.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We should have an audience
with the Queen in two days.</b></Default>

c0000532
00:20:22.890 --> 00:20:24.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, while we await his report,</b></Default>

c0000533
00:20:24.600 --> 00:20:26.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think it's best
to lie low in the city.</b></Default>

c0000534
00:20:26.890 --> 00:20:28.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>All right.</b></Default>

c0000535
00:20:28.310 --> 00:20:29.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SISBELL]
Here's the plan.</b></Default>

c0000536
00:20:29.560 --> 00:20:32.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Iska and I will stake out
the South Altolia station.</b></Default>

c0000537
00:20:32.690 --> 00:20:34.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If assassins are being sent in,</b></Default>

c0000538
00:20:34.570 --> 00:20:37.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>they will likely arrive
by this railroad.</b></Default>

c0000539
00:20:37.530 --> 00:20:41.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A strategy that's equal parts
offense and defense, huh?</b></Default>

c0000540
00:20:41.280 --> 00:20:43.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-One thing...
-Yes.</b></Default>

c0000541
00:20:43.160 --> 00:20:44.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The assassins know my face.</b></Default>

c0000542
00:20:44.910 --> 00:20:47.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Here!
Put this on, and best of luck!</b></Default>

c0000543
00:20:47.750 --> 00:20:49.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[both giggle]</b></Default>

c0000544
00:20:49.580 --> 00:20:51.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And, lastly,
to complete the disguise.</b></Default>

c0000545
00:20:51.710 --> 00:20:53.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Wow, Iska, you look cool!
-[laughing] Nice!</b></Default>

c0000546
00:20:53.590 --> 00:20:55.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yeah, it gives you
an intellectual vibe.</b></Default>

c0000547
00:20:55.800 --> 00:20:57.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And what's my normal vibe?</b></Default>

c0000548
00:20:57.760 --> 00:20:59.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[train whistle blowing]</b></Default>

c0000549
00:20:59.720 --> 00:21:02.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Riesbarten terminal's
South Altoria station.</b></Default>

c0000550
00:21:02.390 --> 00:21:04.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We will be pulling
in there shortly.</b></Default>

c0000551
00:21:04.680 --> 00:21:06.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If Lady Sisbell
were to go into hiding,</b></Default>

c0000552
00:21:06.930 --> 00:21:08.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it would be in this city.</b></Default>

c0000553
00:21:08.810 --> 00:21:11.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you have any idea
of where she might go?</b></Default>

c0000554
00:21:11.100 --> 00:21:13.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If I did, this would be
much easier.</b></Default>

c0000555
00:21:13.520 --> 00:21:14.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But how?</b></Default>

c0000556
00:21:14.360 --> 00:21:17.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>She locks herself away,
stays in her room.</b></Default>

c0000557
00:21:17.360 --> 00:21:19.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't know her habits at all.</b></Default>

c0000558
00:21:19.360 --> 00:21:21.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Not even what she eats.</b></Default>

c0000559
00:21:21.110 --> 00:21:22.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Cake? Or pudding?</b></Default>

c0000560
00:21:22.910 --> 00:21:24.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have no clue.</b></Default>

c0000561
00:21:24.330 --> 00:21:25.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE STATION ANNOUNCER 201A]
We are now arriving</b></Default>

c0000562
00:21:25.490 --> 00:21:27.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>at the South Altoria station.</b></Default>

c0000563
00:21:27.410 --> 00:21:29.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Please ensure that you have...
-[ALICE] Okay, let's go, Rin!</b></Default>

c0000564
00:21:30.000 --> 00:21:31.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wait! Please!</b></Default>

c0000565
00:21:31.290 --> 00:21:34.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You know your baggage is rather
heavy, right, Lady Alice?</b></Default>

c0000566
00:21:34.090 --> 00:21:35.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It'll be quite the challenge.</b></Default>

c0000567
00:21:35.590 --> 00:21:37.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But we'll find
our little Sisbell.</b></Default>

c0000568
00:21:37.130 --> 00:21:40.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Perhaps we can rely on your
extraordinary luck to find her.</b></Default>

c0000569
00:21:40.260 --> 00:21:42.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>After all, you bumped
into that swordsman so often</b></Default>

c0000570
00:21:42.590 --> 00:21:44.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it was nothing short
of uncanny.</b></Default>

c0000571
00:21:44.220 --> 00:21:46.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That was all just coincidence!</b></Default>

c0000572
00:21:46.100 --> 00:21:48.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But yes, it might be fun
to try to guess where Sisbell</b></Default>

c0000573
00:21:48.520 --> 00:21:50.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>might randomly turn up.</b></Default>

c0000574
00:21:50.190 --> 00:21:51.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Like over there!</b></Default>

c0000575
00:21:52.060 --> 00:21:54.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?
You're not serious.</b></Default>

c0000576
00:21:54.230 --> 00:21:56.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's just a juice bar
you see in every terminal.</b></Default>

c0000577
00:21:56.860 --> 00:21:59.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE] With this many people
in here, it's so hot and humid.</b></Default>

c0000578
00:21:59.780 --> 00:22:01.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I think she'd want
to quench her thirst</b></Default>

c0000579
00:22:01.240 --> 00:22:04.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with a refreshing
juice beverage!</b></Default>

c0000580
00:22:04.200 --> 00:22:06.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And it couldn't hurt for us
to hydrate while we're there.</b></Default>

c0000581
00:22:06.780 --> 00:22:09.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Come on,
let's go scope out the place!</b></Default>

c0000582
00:22:09.120 --> 00:22:11.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why the elaborate ruse?
Just say you want juice.</b></Default>

c0000583
00:22:11.710 --> 00:22:14.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was just explaining why
I think she'd want one, too.</b></Default>

c0000584
00:22:15.580 --> 00:22:18.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE] Aw, too bad.
Guess she's not here.</b></Default>

c0000585
00:22:18.210 --> 00:22:19.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>As I might have predicted.</b></Default>

c0000586
00:22:19.880 --> 00:22:22.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Well then, Lady Alice,
what would you like?</b></Default>

c0000587
00:22:22.220 --> 00:22:23.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm, let's see.</b></Default>

c0000588
00:22:24.010 --> 00:22:25.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ah, green smoothie.</b></Default>

c0000589
00:22:25.260 --> 00:22:26.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-'Scuse me.
-Banana juice.</b></Default>

c0000590
00:22:26.970 --> 00:22:28.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Could I have one fresh
strawberry... -Ooh, a fresh</b></Default>

c0000591
00:22:28.270 --> 00:22:30.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-strawberry shake sounds nice,
or... -...shake and also...</b></Default>

c0000592
00:22:30.230 --> 00:22:31.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Let's see.
-[ALICE] Right, got it.</b></Default>

c0000593
00:22:31.520 --> 00:22:34.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[TOGETHER] Melon soda
with special coconut ice cream,</b></Default>

c0000594
00:22:34.400 --> 00:22:35.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>topped with fresh whipped cream</b></Default>

c0000595
00:22:35.770 --> 00:22:37.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and a swirl
of the enderflower syrup.</b></Default>

c0000596
00:22:37.980 --> 00:22:39.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ah? Oh?</b></Default>

c0000597
00:22:40.690 --> 00:22:41.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh!</b></Default>

c0000598
00:22:43.360 --> 00:22:44.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Hold on...
-It's you.</b></Default>

